<item>
            <title>[LU-44] e2fsprogs&apos; configure does not detect when there is no db.h available</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-44</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If you don&apos;t have a db-devel package installed and therefore have a db.h available, configure detects it but does not error out:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;checking db.h usability... no&lt;br/&gt;
checking db.h presence... no&lt;br/&gt;
checking for db.h... no&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But db.h is required for lfsck.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="10268">LU-44</key>
            <summary>e2fsprogs&apos; configure does not detect when there is no db.h available</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
